               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>These Regulations may be cited as the Public Procurement etc. (Scotland) (Amendment) (EU Exit) Amendment Regulations 2019.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-1-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>These Regulations come into force immediately before exit day.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
